snippet.textDisplay:
✨ Heartfelt thanks to Coke Studio India 🙏 – you are giving a new identity and respect to India’s diverse languages and folk music in the modern era. Truly a proud moment for every music lover. ❤️🎶

Did you know?
➡️ Maithili language is spoken by nearly 80 million people across India and Nepal.
➡️ Maithili folk music (Vidyapati Geet, Sohar, Jhijhiya, Samdaun) is a priceless treasure of our culture and heritage.

🌸 On behalf of all Maithili speakers, a humble request – please dedicate a space to Maithili folk music on this platform someday.
It will not only be an emotional and historic moment for us, but will also enrich the diversity of Indian music even more. 🙌

👉 “Folk music is our soul, and language is our identity.” 🇮🇳
Long live Indian folk music, long live our mother tongues! ✨
